These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, bellflower
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
2 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
1. the person who growslily is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Flower       | bellflower       | lily |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| Pet       | hedgehog    | bird    |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
House: colonial, victorian
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, lawyer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, time-travel
2 different games are played: backgammon, whist
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| House      | victorian     | colonial |
| Job           | entrepreneur | lawyer      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | action      |
| Game         | backgammon | whist     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, tiparillo
There 2 different types of food: apple, avocado
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
The people have 2 different jobs:  scientist, firefighter
1. the fan of country is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is the firefighter##1
3. the person eating apple is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Cigar      | aristoff | tiparillo  |
| Food          | apple    | avocado   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   |
| Job     | firefighter     | scientist |

