2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
There are 2 different nationalities: american, malaysian
1. the coach is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
2. the coach is on the right of the malaysian##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| Color   | blue          | orange |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| Nationality     | malaysian            | american       |

 